com.cmput301f17t07.ingroove.DataManagers.Command

Class AddHabitEventCommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cmput301f17t07.ingroove.DataManagers.Command.ServerCommand
      • com.cmput301f17t07.ingroove.DataManagers.Command.AddHabitEventCommand

  • public class AddHabitEventCommand
extends ServerCommand
    [Command Class] AddHabitEvent command subclasses ServerCommmand and represents a command object containing all the data for a new habitEvent to be added for a particular user. It also contains a reference to its receiver which does the work of adding the habitEvent when execute() is called.
    See Also:
    ServerCommandManager, Created by Christopher Walter on 2017-11-09.
